{"tid":1709614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實一年前大家就應該要發現 錯嘅唔係老闆 係打工仔","createTime":"2019-11-12T02:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T06:19:07.000Z","uid":97503,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8a00117794927958ae9053537c74c40c94f7f765","tid":1709614,"uid":97503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Knkm0Sb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnkm0Sb.jpg&h=dc48e55e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一年前大家仲講緊打工仔乜慘物慘 末日都要&rdquo;被迫&rdquo;返工<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NHzfkSd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHzfkSd.png&h=05ea45ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家再睇下今日 一班打工仔為咗返工去到幾撚盡 一年前大家就應該要發現 根本係依班香港人奴性太重 根本已經唔需要老闆去出聲 自己都會想盡辦法返工<br />\n<br />\n依兩日想盡辦法返工嘅人 唔該你好好諗下行返工嘅嗰段路踐踏緊幾多人嘅生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec412b51016b67a6cae846b89831b83529ac92c7","tid":1709614,"uid":97503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:40:38.000Z","msg":"係咪已經冇嘢可以阻止到佢哋返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08a8acc0d4c793ef46e26f3b0a5ac081e014d4b","tid":1709614,"uid":278414,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:41:37.000Z","msg":"777今日都寸緊熱愛返工既港豬"},{"pid":"340af248a1f96ccf185133c3c1849b757cf016b9","tid":1709614,"uid":122275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:42:24.000Z","msg":"唔返工佢地仲有咩價值？"},{"pid":"ea91a18d69d5465c95ba51da1af1e4bafc4224bb","tid":1709614,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"340af248a1f96ccf185133c3c1849b757cf016b9","tid":1709614,"uid":122275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:42:24.000Z","msg":"唔返工佢地仲有咩價值？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:43:10.000Z","msg":"佢地以為有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d74a18f095a514b7131d4064b5a00d3ca4d349b","tid":1709614,"uid":296677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"340af248a1f96ccf185133c3c1849b757cf016b9","tid":1709614,"uid":122275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:42:24.000Z","msg":"唔返工佢地仲有咩價值？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:43:23.000Z","msg":"返工係佢哋嘅核心價值"},{"pid":"8c60263d99774c371bc0027d986e425e4d3cf6b1","tid":1709614,"uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:45:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">返工是香港人的最核心價值, 比自由民主更重要, 大家必須接受呢個事實</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c7c8a50bcee23aeb9084e6b2efa0d9702675f7d1","tid":1709614,"uid":118945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:50:10.000Z","msg":"香港都無埋嘅時候<br />\n返工有乜意義⋯<br />\n錢，做譚仔啊姐都唔少"},{"pid":"7ba5fb351a4016c6cef0cad310e125a885e9680a","tid":1709614,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=5f8e12ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a>"},{"pid":"1d0e38228d58f0c21d1c33ca246a168f00fcf1b2","tid":1709614,"uid":302814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:12:01.000Z","msg":"世界上無野可阻到香港人返工<br />\n唔返工就少左一日糧就供唔到樓就跑少日數就升遲過同儕 習慣屈服既香港人係自私的 只要搞唔到我身邊我就不會反抗"},{"pid":"e62a552312e31fe1e155fa91d6c368db1de2d1e0","tid":1709614,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:45:12.000Z","msg":"老闆話唔使返，都實會有幾個死都照返扮勤力1<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2726f64dc41b3c53fd703f2ff3e2725e5cb4ce3c","tid":1709614,"uid":84275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:59:10.000Z","msg":"行返埋站唔代表繼續返工，我都有fd係車上要落車行返去車站，之後返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行返車站係因為安全問題架車開唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1f5867e72760c8faa0e7aa520fecef6113e678","tid":1709614,"uid":39668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ba5fb351a4016c6cef0cad310e125a885e9680a","tid":1709614,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=5f8e12ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"請大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好再入</span>呢個樹窿<br />\n<br />\nAdmin K叔私底下性騷擾會員﹑<br />\nAdmin Karma一句意見不合就可以踢你出group，<br />\n一方面係連登開post一方面叫人唔好睇咁多連登<br />\n至今叫admin出黎解釋半個月可以無回應，比林鄭更林鄭。<br />\n<br />\n風頭火勢之時唔代表我會唔再追擊，搵仔Group已經ban左希望下個就到你"}]}